name: Steampunk Neo Victorian Antique Bronze Leaf Sprig Pocket Watch Pendant
description:
Very romantic antiqued bronze leaf sprig is sitting on an antique pocket watch pendant. Truly amazing!! Mounted onto a vintage key and hangs from a pretty 22" antiqued bronze soldered link chain.

Measures 1.25" wide by 1.5" long, chain can be made shorter or longer if you prefer.

name: Steampunk Neo Victorian Silver Aviator Wings Antique Watch Necklace
description:
So cool!! Antique ladies watch is set on an antique New York Standard Watch Co. pocket watch piece and set with angel wings in silver. !! Hangs from a 20" silver plated soldered link chain. I love it!!

Measures 2" wide by 1.75" long

name: https://www.etsy.com/listing/128592628/steampunk-victorian-dragonfly-antique?ref=shop_home_active

Playful antiqued bronze dragonfly is set a top an antique pocket watch pendant and embellished with antique gears and watch parts! Very beautiful one-of-a-kind piece! Hangs a vintage key on a 24" antiqued bronze soldered link chain. Chain can be longer or shorter upon request.

Measures 1.75" long by 1.25" wide

name: Steampunk Victorian Pretty Silver Swallow Antique Pocket Watch Pendant
description:

Measures approx. 1.5" wide and 2" long. Chain can be made shorter if you prefer.
